Output terminal/rendered/01-welcome-scope.mp4
Output terminal/rendered/01-welcome-scope.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 22ms
Set Padding 20

Type "# Datadog Drilldown"
Enter
Sleep 250ms
Type "# RCA + DICE + optional QUBO enricher"
Enter
Type "# Same incident report: text propositions + telemetry + solver glue"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Type "# Embabel agents · Datadog telemetry · test-report-server"
Enter
Sleep 2s
